{"tid":2136111,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"騙徒冒衞署發信套行蹤","createTime":"2020-08-02T01:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T01:31:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"21f5b7ffd5d503b1dbbd78485c594df44c7922b7","tid":2136111,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T01:31:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200802/4Z2RYRKR5XNW6SOQUDDZKWNDPI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200802%2F4Z2RYRKR5XNW6SOQUDDZKWNDPI%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnUPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=9bb90864\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200802%2F4Z2RYRKR5XNW6SOQUDDZKWNDPI%2F&h=c8f7c163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200802/4Z2RYRKR5XNW6SOQUDDZKWNDPI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n騙徒冒衞署發信套行蹤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dXqXP9t3UazTfxugblBcI3GHAPg=/369x523/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BESEB6NCXRRHYDQ66PB3KHSROU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdXqXP9t3UazTfxugblBcI3GHAPg%3D%2F369x523%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBESEB6NCXRRHYDQ66PB3KHSROU.gif&h=e6d3e0f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大埔區議員任啟邦指有街坊收到假冒衞生署信件。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】大埔有市民近日收到自稱衞生署發出的信件，聲稱某住戶已確診，要求鄰居舉報其行蹤。衞生防護中心昨澄清信件是假冒衞生署，署方追蹤確診患者「唔會周圍問街坊」。區議員懷疑是有人借疫情行騙或收數。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：亞博啟用收30患者 走廊漏水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n區議員質疑藉疫情收數<br />\n<br />\n大埔富善邨區議員任啟邦在facebook表示，有街坊收到一封有衞生署標誌的信件，內容稱因未能找到已確診的某單位住戶，要求鄰居提供該住戶行蹤，信上附上一個手提電話號碼。任啟邦指信件可疑，亦有不少錯字，懷疑有人藉疫情行騙或收數。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君昨澄清，衞生署追蹤確診患者「唔會周圍問街坊」，亦不會用信件方式了解患者行蹤，提醒市民小心。<br />\n<br />\n另外，醫管局總行政經理何。。。。。。。。。。。。。。紅十字會捐血服務中心亦已徹底消毒及採取防感染措施，確保捐血者及血液安全。"}]}